15
00:01:00,460 --> 00:01:03,293
<i>... the divide between rich and poor</i>
<i>became so great...</i>

16
00:01:03,463 --> 00:01:06,455
<i>... it ignited the fuse</i>
<i>of a new rebellion.</i>

17
00:01:07,901 --> 00:01:09,391
<i>The push for independence...</i>

18
00:01:09,569 --> 00:01:11,196
<i>... exploded into the streets.</i>

19
00:01:11,404 --> 00:01:14,965
<i>Armed freedom fighters pitted</i>
<i>themselves against their government...</i>

20
00:01:15,141 --> 00:01:17,735
<i>... now controlled by the oligarchs.</i>

21
00:01:19,045 --> 00:01:21,275
<i>The military prospered</i>
<i>during this time...</i>

22
00:01:21,448 --> 00:01:24,042
<i>... becoming ever stronger</i>
<i>and better equipped.</i>

23
00:01:24,217 --> 00:01:26,412
<i>Under the guidance</i>
<i>of Ivan Judanovich...</i>

24
00:01:26,586 --> 00:01:28,747
<i>... an Ataman</i>
<i>from the Council of Elders...</i>

25
00:01:28,922 --> 00:01:30,947
<i>... the freedom fighters</i>
<i>moved their base...</i>

26
00:01:31,424 --> 00:01:32,789
<i>... to a hidden location.</i>

27
00:01:32,992 --> 00:01:35,460
<i>A more suitable place to launch...</i>

28
00:01:35,628 --> 00:01:38,062
<i>... their guerrilla war</i>
<i>against the government.</i>

29
00:01:39,799 --> 00:01:42,324
<i>After several years</i>
<i>of brutal fighting...</i>

30
00:01:42,502 --> 00:01:44,436
<i>... it was Svetlana Belikova...</i>

31
00:01:44,604 --> 00:01:46,902
<i>... Eastern Slav's</i>
<i>first female president...</i>

32
00:01:47,073 --> 00:01:50,236
<i>... who offered a ceasefire</i>
<i>to the freedom fighters.</i>

33
00:01:51,911 --> 00:01:54,436
<i>But the break from hostilities</i>
<i>was short-lived.</i>

34
00:01:54,614 --> 00:01:57,447
<i>In November of 2010,</i>
<i>the government discovered...</i>

35
00:01:57,617 --> 00:02:00,450
<i>... that the rebels' land</i>
<i>contained valuable resources.</i>

36
00:02:00,620 --> 00:02:02,645
<i>The military continued</i>
<i>their attacks...</i>

37
00:02:02,822 --> 00:02:05,290
<i>... claiming they were</i>
<i>fighting terrorism.</i>

38
00:02:06,326 --> 00:02:09,523
<i>Losing one base after another</i>
<i>to the military's onslaught...</i>

39
00:02:09,696 --> 00:02:12,324
<i>... the freedom fighters</i>
<i>escalated their efforts...</i>

40
00:02:12,499 --> 00:02:15,263
<i>... and became more and more</i>
<i>radical in their tactics.</i>

41
00:02:15,502 --> 00:02:17,299
<i>It was then that strange rumors...</i>

42
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:20,098
<i>... began spreading like wildfire</i>
<i>among the people...</i>

43
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:22,670
<i>... that monsters had joined the battle.</i>

44
00:02:23,910 --> 00:02:25,775
<i>In February of 2011...</i>

45
00:02:25,945 --> 00:02:28,675
<i>... the rumors made it to</i>
<i>the old city of Holifgrad...</i>

46
00:02:28,848 --> 00:02:31,715
<i>... just a few kilometers</i>
<i>from the Presidential Palace...</i>

47
00:02:31,918 --> 00:02:34,853
<i>... an important strategic location</i>
<i>for the government.</i>

48
00:02:48,501 --> 00:02:52,198
<i>Listen to the words of the elders.</i>

49
00:02:53,006 --> 00:02:57,534
<i>We have finally gained</i>
