51
00:03:03,883 --> 00:03:05,544
<i>Gather, people.</i>

52
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:09,686
<i>Gather and fight.</i>

53
00:03:10,590 --> 00:03:13,684
<i>Fight for independence!</i>

54
