<i>- Do not resist arrest.</i>
- Retreat!

57
00:03:34,047 --> 00:03:35,173
<i>Drop your weapons.</i>

58
00:03:35,348 --> 00:03:36,713
<i>- Surrender immediately.</i>
- Government pigs!

59
00:03:36,883 --> 00:03:39,408
<i>I repeat, do not resist arrest.</i>

60
00:03:39,619 --> 00:03:41,780
<i>Surrender immediately.</i>

61
00:04:02,442 --> 00:04:04,205
Moving into position.

62
