Looks like they're doing some
serious renovations down here.

67
00:04:29,469 --> 00:04:31,266
<i>Listen to me carefully, Leon.</i>

68
00:04:31,437 --> 00:04:33,302
<i>Your mission has been aborted.</i>

69
00:04:33,473 --> 00:04:36,237
<i>The U.S. Is going to pull out</i>
<i>of the country.</i>

70
00:04:36,409 --> 00:04:38,434
