74
00:04:43,983 --> 00:04:47,919
<i>Washington and the government there</i>
<i>have decided to go their separate ways.</i>

75
00:04:48,087 --> 00:04:50,453
<i>Everyone has to leave,</i>
<i>not just embassy staff.</i>

76
00:04:50,623 --> 00:04:54,423
<i>All American citizens have been</i>
<i>ordered to evacuate the country.</i>

77
00:04:54,627 --> 00:04:56,492
I don't give a damn
about the politics.

78
00:04:56,663 --> 00:04:59,962
