and things are different.

83
00:05:08,675 --> 00:05:12,008
No one can do anything without backup
from the American government.

84
00:05:12,178 --> 00:05:13,202
Not even you.

85
00:05:13,379 --> 00:05:16,143
Well, then I guess
my only option is to...

86
00:05:16,316 --> 00:05:18,716
...lose my American
citizenship for a while.

87
00:05:18,885 --> 00:05:19,874
<i>Leon!</i>

88
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:23,153
She can tell them I got lost
and missed my flight.

89
00:06:00,059 --> 00:06:01,890
Better hurry up and get this done.

90
00:06:02,061 --> 00:06:03,858
I need some breakfast.

91
00:07:00,086 --> 00:07:01,383
Scarecrow.

92
00:07:01,554 --> 00:07:03,317
I'm the Tin Man.
Can you talk?

93
00:07:05,558 --> 00:07:09,392
What's the connection between the
anti-government forces and the B.O.W.s?

94
00:07:12,432 --> 00:07:14,400
I guess scarecrows
aren't known...

95
00:07:14,567 --> 00:07:16,125
...for rousing
conversation.

96
00:07:17,403 --> 00:07:18,392
Hang in there.

97
00:07:18,571 --> 00:07:19,970
I'll get you out of here.

98
00:07:20,139 --> 00:07:21,572
Bee...

99
00:07:23,910 --> 00:07:25,241
What?

100
00:07:25,778 --> 00:07:26,836
Say that again.

101
00:07:27,580 --> 00:07:28,774
Bee...

102
00:07:29,315 --> 00:07:31,715
...keeper.
- Beekeeper?

103
00:07:33,719 --> 00:07:35,983
The honeybee I saw outside.

104
00:07:48,434 --> 00:07:51,335
Great. Now I got
a cowardly lion to deal with.

105
