It's the army.

106
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,809
Is anyone here?

107
00:10:20,953 --> 00:10:22,614
Check the room down there.

108
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:31,824
Hey...

109
00:10:32,598 --> 00:10:34,691
Don't say a word.

110
00:10:37,436 --> 00:10:39,301
How about that one?

111
00:10:53,719 --> 00:10:55,710
This one's clear.

112
