...don't push that button.

214
00:16:31,023 --> 00:16:33,218
I'm not falling for that.

215
00:16:33,392 --> 00:16:35,553
No way I'll allow them
to trace the call.

216
00:16:43,769 --> 00:16:45,202
How are things out there?

217
00:16:45,371 --> 00:16:48,397
Looks like they have the old part
of the city surrounded.

218
00:16:48,640 --> 00:16:50,972
We'd better wait and see
how things pan out.

219
00:16:52,478 --> 00:16:54,412
<i>Bio Organic Weapons.</i>

220
00:16:54,580 --> 00:16:56,172
<i>Also known as...</i>

221
00:16:56,348 --> 00:16:57,975
...B.O.W.s.

222
00:16:58,150 --> 00:17:01,176
Most developed countries
and the United Nations...

223
00:17:01,353 --> 00:17:04,880
...are against the use
and manufacture of B.O.W.s.

224
00:17:05,057 --> 00:17:07,389
However, they are, unfortunately...

225
00:17:07,559 --> 00:17:10,153
...still traded on
the world's black markets.

226
