There's no way to differentiate...

230
00:17:20,939 --> 00:17:22,907
...between friend and foe.

231
00:17:23,075 --> 00:17:25,043
It is true that total control...

232
00:17:25,210 --> 00:17:27,269
...of most of the B.O.W.s...

233
00:17:27,446 --> 00:17:30,108
...has been nearly impossible
up until now.

234
00:17:30,616 --> 00:17:34,279
But a new technology
that changes that fact...

235
00:17:34,453 --> 00:17:36,921
...has recently been developed.

236
00:17:38,123 --> 00:17:39,351
Tell me more.

237
00:17:40,259 --> 00:17:42,284
Recent technological
advancements...

238
00:17:42,461 --> 00:17:46,295
...can establish
a master/slave relationship...

239
00:17:46,465 --> 00:17:49,525
...between a human and the B.O.W.s.

240
00:17:49,735 --> 00:17:50,759
So?

241
00:17:50,936 --> 00:17:52,801
